story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_0300_10: (Our priority should be keeping everyone safe...)
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_0400_10:
(But if worst comes to worst, I might have to forgo
protecting the Ultra Beasts.)
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_0600_10:
Raichu isn’t the only one that’s gotten stronger
from the island challenge!
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_0700_10: I’m definitely gonna help the Ultra Beasts!
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_1100_10:
I can’t believe Old Hala, of all people, lost
confidence in himself.
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_1400_10:
Is it appearing during this island’s crisis to fulfill
its role as a guardian deity?
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_1600_10: I don’t know why it’s here, but...
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_1700_10: I guess that doesn’t matter. Hear me, Tapu Koko!
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_1800_10:
I wanna help everyone on Pasio...and the
Ultra Beasts, too!
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_2100_10: Looks like Tapu Koko feels the same!
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_2200_10: It wants to fight together with you.
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_2300_10:
Are you sure you’re OK choosing me and
not gramps?
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_2400_10: Hau’s heart is far stronger than mine!
story_alola_01_09000/2401_1001_2500_10: OK! Let’s do this, Tapu Koko!
